message: >-
  If you use Parametric Concept Memory (PCM) — either the framework
  code or the four-domain empirical findings — in academic work,
  please cite the release below.
type: software
title: "Parametric Concept Memory (PCM)"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: 2026-04-22
